Answe:  
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Physics wallha</title>
    <style>@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?
family=Poppins:wght@200;400;500&display=swap");
body {
    text-align: centter;
}
h1{
    font-family:"poppins", sans-serif;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 40px;
}
p {
    font-family: "poppins",sans-serif;
    padding: 10px 15%;
}
    
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>About us</h1>
<p>PW Skills' mission is to permeate through every student/professional's outlook towards
jobs and change their attitude and perspective from "How Can I Do It?" to "Of Course I Can Do
It". We aim to do this by providing
